Title: The BEST LTM in Apex Legends History!
Description: The BEST LTM in Apex Legends History. Apex Legends News. Apex Leaks. Apex Easter Eggs. Apex Legends Nostalgia.  DUMMIEs Big Day LTM released in Apex Legends in Season 3 during the Grand Soiree Arcade Event. Within the Grand Soiree Collection Event, 7 LTMS were released, including Gold Rush Duos, Third-Person Mode, Always Be Closing, DUMMIEs Big Day, and After Dark regular battle royale modes for both World‚Äôs Edge and King‚Äôs Canyon.  Within the DUMMIE's Big Day game mode, every player was a DUMMIE and had the same abilities.  The DUMMIEs Tactical spawned a random piece of loot for you or your teammate.  The DUMMIEs had 3 Ultimate Abilities: Emergency Loot Pinata, Emergency Dance Party (which is now Mirage's Ultimate), and Emergency Area Heal. Title: What If Apex Legends Had 1st Person Finishers?
Description: What If Apex Legends Had 1st Person Finishers? Apex Legends News. Apex Leaks. Apex Legends Mods.  Performing Finishers in Apex Legends is a quick way to get back your Shields and to increase your EVO amount, but what if Finishers within Apex Legends were in 1st Person view rather than the normal 3rd Person view?  With the power of R5 Reloaded, a modded version of Apex Legends, we can see 1st Person Finishers for Legends such as Lifeline, Caustic, Mirage, and Loba!  Different Finishers within Apex Legends, including Legendary Finishers, always show the enemy and the Legend performing the finisher in the Third Person, despite Apex Legends being played in First Person! Title: Top 5 Fastest Finishers in Apex Legends!
